              <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono font-medium min-w-[60px]">2020</span>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-h4 text-text-primary group-hover:text-flank transition-colors">Conference on Digital Experimentation (CODE) @ MIT</h3>
                <p class="text-body text-text-secondary mt-1">Discovering heterogeneity of treatment effects in conjoint experiments</p>
